{"tid":1384283,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"新加坡廢老排隊買優惠手機   華為備貨嚴重不足報警拉人","createTime":"2019-07-30T01:07:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-30T10:46:36.000Z","uid":202464,"like":21,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"8bfb689b7f79ae67aa22a59cc2657c880a1b6c73","tid":1384283,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T01:07:23.000Z","msg":"新加坡早前 54 週年國慶，華為推出長者買機優惠，只要年滿 50 歲的新加坡永久居民，就可以 54 新加坡元購買原價 198 新加坡元的 Y6 Pro 2019 手機，每人限購最多兩部。<br />\n<br />\n華為起初宣傳時指促銷活動會持續數天，不過為了搶平貨，不少長者在促銷活動當日凌晨 4 時，就已經在華為的專門店外排隊等候。不過隨後這些長者才發現，每家專門店準備的 Y6 Pro 2019 存貨只有 20 至 30 部。有排在第 16 位的長者表示，當排第 12 位的顧客步入商店，工作人員就宣佈所有手機售罄。<br />\n<br />\n及後華為更張貼告示，指全線 27 家分店的所有促銷手機都售罄。華為備貨太少引起漏夜排隊的長者不滿，其中一名 53 歲的女士甚至拒絕離開店舖。店員隨後報警，警方到場後以非法侵入罪將女士拘捕。"},{"pid":"872fff4f3b027497f124bd17a76fd07e1cfface7","tid":1384283,"uid":57012,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T01:15:54.000Z","msg":"傻系黎既"},{"pid":"c3154f87d1b3ab02d1d5c4a837542c66a5883433","tid":1384283,"uid":105782,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T01:16:41.000Z","msg":"50歲都叫長者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ecbe0e3de7a6c87b1c6723262d270cc561533d2","tid":1384283,"uid":266231,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T01:16:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"00fa58bea8ca761733ba7eeba777ea8b357e7610","tid":1384283,"uid":47674,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T01:20:08.000Z","msg":"&quot;警方到場後以非法侵入罪將女士拘捕&quot;<br />\n<br />\n這就是新加坡.jpg<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4125102fc7fe5b21719335a501816e4615426740","tid":1384283,"uid":104165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T01:21:06.000Z","msg":"新加坡人好劣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf1bfde39551fe887036a98f7e98321e40857b84","tid":1384283,"uid":258340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T01:26:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2d0f61701988a23a29e45c996237086bf6b9776","tid":1384283,"uid":4574,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T01:28:25.000Z","msg":"新加坡= 富貴版北韓"},{"pid":"6b03c729b2258ad7062f4a603572f4cece312f4e","tid":1384283,"uid":155095,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"c2d0f61701988a23a29e45c996237086bf6b9776","tid":1384283,"uid":4574,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T01:28:25.000Z","msg":"新加坡= 富貴版北韓"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T05:59:08.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">等於英文版中華人民共和國</span></strong>"},{"pid":"5d616b523c0da22c3c1647eb5a2b1fb947b2be53","tid":1384283,"uid":202464,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T10:46:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>新加坡= 富貴版北韓</blockquote><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">等於英文版中華人民共和國</span></strong></blockquote><br />\n的確係進化版支那。<br />\n<br />\n坡人去到香港都唔敢批評佢地政府。"}]}